cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.CY 

This paper is about building adaptive natural language interfaces through interaction, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper discusses strategies for learning language from scratch, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.AI and cs.LG). The paper also involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and the use of a game to collect data (cs.CY).
